      • tryAndParse

        void tryAndParse​(simplenet.Client client,

      • createHeaders

        java.lang.String createHeaders()
        Creates default headers for generateRequest(String). By default, this is: 
             HTTP/1.1 200 OK
     Server: EmojIDE
     Content-Length: [dynamic]
     Content-Type: text/html
     Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
     Connection: Closed
        Returns:
        The headers
